dc_description_s: This collection of data is produced by the California Office of Statewide Health and Planning. It contains vector shapefile data about workflorce shortages in primary care, mental health professionals, dental professionals, and registered nurses, as well as data related to medically underserved areas and populations. System requirements: Geographic Information Systems (GIS) software that reads ESRI shapefile format.
dc_publisher_s: California Office of Statewide Health and Planning Department.
dc_creator_sm: California Office of Statewide Health Planning and Development
